keyFacts: This is a transcription request form from the DOJ Office of the Inspector General Investigations Division.
The form is for an audio interview recorded on March 16, 2022, lasting 53 minutes and 39 seconds.
The associated case number is 2019010614, and the estimated transcript length is 74 pages.
The form indicates the request was approved and provides cost estimates for the transcription service.
No specific individuals, victims, or subjects are named in this administrative form.
